2.2 Junior Knight:
------------------

Dillon           6  11   6   2   7   5   9   (46!)
                 Small Guns, Repair, Science
                 Gifted, Glowing One
                 Sharpshooter, Better Criticals (Perk Rate 4)

He has a great perception and luck, but he is missing 1 stat point (Gifted
