4.4 Paladin Commander:
----------------------

Jim          10   5   8   2   5   8   2   (40)
             Big Guns, Energy Weapons, Throwing
             Fast Shot, Vat Skin
             Bonus Rate of Fire, Steady Arm, Hit the Deck,
             Tough Hide (Perk Rate 4)

